item.title: Compile error 100 errors
item.dc:creator: @izin8r2296 izin8r2296
item.description:
@izin8r2296 wrote:

That’s a very annoying error. It’s pretty easy to fix, though.

Get your original source, if you’re using one. Then, find the part in client.java you edited, and replace it with that part in the source’s client.java

Easily fixed.

And by the way, post this in the compiling sticky
